<P>
A Yorba Linda bicyclist was fatally injured Tuesday when he was struck by a 
car, police said. 
</P>
<P>
Charles Randall Bright, 61, was pronounced dead at the scene after being struck 
by a car driven by Julie Schaefer, 18, of Yorba Linda, police said. 
</P>
<P>
No citation was issued pending an investigation of the accident, which occurred 
at 3:50 p.m. at the intersection of Village Center Drive and Via Marwah, police 
said. 
</P>
